'''Skip 5''' was an [[Asteroid/Legends|asteroid]] in the [[Smuggler's Run/Legends|Smuggler's Run]].<ref name="The New Rebellion">''[[The New Rebellion]]''</ref> It was the [[Homeworld/Legends|homeworld]] of the [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Jedi Knight]] [[Traavis]].<ref name="Order 66: Destroy All Jedi">{{InsiderCite|87|Order 66: Destroy All Jedi}}</ref>

It was very hot, with an internal temperature that was about 40 centigrade that made it almost unbearable for most [[Species/Legends|species]]. As a result, it was abandoned during the time that [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] was a regular on the Run. About a decade before, it was occupied by a group of [[Smuggler/Legends|smugglers]], who lived there for months, but eventually ended up killing each other in a fight that was supposedly started by the heat.<ref name="The New Rebellion" />

In around [[17 ABY/Legends|17 ABY]], [[Jawa/Legends|Jawas]] were brought there to help repair damaged [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] equipment that the smugglers were smuggling for the [[Dark Jedi/Legends|Dark Jedi]] [[Kueller]]. It was presumably damaged after [[Droid/Legends|droids]] with explosives in them, that were bound for [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]], were detonated by Kueller.<ref name="The New Rebellion" />

